title: Which is India’s most anti-national news outlet? I’ll start.
selftext:
https://theprint.in/opinion/india-canada-must-strategise-against-khalistan-supporters-without-silencing-peaceful-critics/1772162/

For me, it’s The Print. I don’t know if they’re only anti-BJP, but I’ve seen them regularly post anti-national content.
